Galactic Turtle 1.1.1 2008-09-07
--------------------------------
 * Use pkg-config to determine the location of sqlite3 during compilation. This
   should allow Galactic Turtle to build on more POSIX systems (e.g. FreeBSD).

Galactic Turtle 1.1.0 2008-09-07
--------------------------------
 * Switched to Autotools.
 * Added --version switch.

Galactic Turtle 1.0.1 2008-08-02
--------------------------------
 * Fix incompatibility with GCC 4.3.

Galactic Turtle 1.0.0 2008-05-08
--------------------------------
 * Initial release.
